Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.02,0:20:28.47,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}You held out a small hand
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:34.36,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Smiling like to you it was so natural
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:39.53,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}It may have no meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:45.30,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}but it is something I cannot do
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.63,0:20:51.37,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}You touched my hand without thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.37,0:20:55.16,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}but it was nice for me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.09,0:21:03.48,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}All the time we believed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.60,0:21:08.96,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}that the world was in our hands
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.15,0:21:11.86,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}We were wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.86,0:21:19.93,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}maybe it wasn't 'cause \Nyou're holding my hand now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.93,0:21:25.55,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}At every moment
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.66,0:21:31.09,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.19,0:21:36.42,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}I can believe, I can believe
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.75,0:21:41.60,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}When I'm holding your warm hand
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.66,0:21:48.97,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}your warm hand
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.02,0:20:28.47,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}你伸出的手稚氣未脫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:34.36,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}宛若唇邊淺淺的笑渦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:39.53,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}它於無意中動人心魄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.76,0:20:45.30,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}無緣的我卻徒添寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.63,0:20:51.37,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}你漫不經心地觸碰我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.37,0:20:55.16,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}殊不知暖流浸滿我的心頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.09,0:21:03.48,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}回首昔日  我們堅信不疑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.60,0:21:08.96,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}手中所握  便是一樹菩提
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.15,0:21:11.86,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}陰差陽錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.86,0:21:19.93,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}這一刻  世界也融化於你雙手的溫熱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.93,0:21:25.55,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}無時無刻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.66,0:21:31.09,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}不論何處
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.19,0:21:36.42,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}我的信仰  堅守不渝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.75,0:21:41.60,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}請讓我貪戀你手心的溫度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.66,0:21:48.97,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}手心的溫度
